column1: #dig start(30; 30; Center tile of a 59-tile square!) This is a 59x59 layout of countless small apartments; the design "cribbed from the wiki" by Meeker. It's HUGE! I like the 3-tile wide corridors. And the 3x3 solid center leaves room to build taodih's 3x3 counter-clockwise spiral ramp staircase.
